title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show OCT-07-2013 MON
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show OCT-07-2013 MON









Prager 20131007  3 Give It Up

Prager H3: Mark Isler fills in for Dennis and is joined by Victor David Hanson,
 National Review Columnist, 

    who gives a less than optimistic view at the upcoming elections for the GOP.


Prager 20131007  What Can Be Done

Prager H2: Mark Isler fills in for Dennis. 
 Mark attended the California Republican Convention and it gave him hope
 for the future of the party.

 Jim Brulte, former CA Senate Republican Leader joins the show to discuss 
  the upcoming elections and how to win.


Prager 20131007  Will the Cookie Crumble?

Prager H1: Mark Isler fills in for Dennis and addresses Obamacare and 
  the likelihood that it may crumble under its own weight.
